<B>__{on mantan}
<A>__{he's human after all, and he does hear the boos. don't let those athletes in the papers fool you. you hear the boos and nobody, nobody except dennis rodman likes to be booed. mantan is getting rattled. on mau mau's box sloan rushes into the box and they are quiet. they don't have to say or shout a thing. the rough apollo crowd is doing it all themselves.}
